{"tid":651481,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"運動新手求意見","createTime":"2018-05-03T06:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T04:31:04.000Z","uid":24982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cecbf64437a342209c15b08e0a29a3421e6ef29a","tid":651481,"uid":24982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"近排想做運動，想問下各位高人嘅意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我主要想跑步，因為唔洗book場，又搵唔到朋友一齊，跑步可以自己一個。<br />\n想跑步原因主要係想增強健體，因為我發覺我身體真係好差，而家廿頭，但行快兩步都好易喘氣，有時會無啦啦有少少頭痛頭暈咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就唔係想減肥嘅，因為我好瘦。<br />\n<br />\n想問下<br />\n1. 如果我跑步應該咩時間跑？暫時早晚都可以。我會喺公園跑，想知係咪朝早植物釋放氧氣，晚上釋放二氧化碳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 我應該跑幾耐？同埋應該都係慢跑開始？<br />\n3. 仲有無咩特別嘅野要主意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4de1a295d945e949e18f8695ba4f9e26f813e55","tid":651481,"uid":124260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"1. 最好既梗係朝早跑<br />\n2. 未跑過就慢跑短距離, 慢慢再加上去<br />\n3. 最好有目標, 唔係好快放棄"},{"pid":"1d47fa9e4e1f53c4117bd49ce08cd1d79a02faca","tid":651481,"uid":24982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4de1a295d945e949e18f8695ba4f9e26f813e55","tid":651481,"uid":124260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"1. 最好既梗係朝早跑<br />\n2. 未跑過就慢跑短距離, 慢慢再加上去<br />\n3. 最好有目標, 唔係好快放棄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:44:36.000Z","msg":"朝早跑係5點左右？因為望住個天慢慢光好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目標唔知應該點set<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> set時間？<br />\n因為我好怕我會好易放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07b396326fb538ef31cf47909098dc5ad3cc9f8","tid":651481,"uid":124260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d47fa9e4e1f53c4117bd49ce08cd1d79a02faca","tid":651481,"uid":24982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4de1a295d945e949e18f8695ba4f9e26f813e55","tid":651481,"uid":124260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:41:11.000Z","msg":"1. 最好既梗係朝早跑<br />\n2. 未跑過就慢跑短距離, 慢慢再加上去<br />\n3. 最好有目標, 唔係好快放棄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T06:44:36.000Z","msg":"朝早跑係5點左右？因為望住個天慢慢光好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目標唔知應該點set<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> set時間？<br />\n因為我好怕我會好易放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"咁易放棄最好搵人捉你去跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4251ee7e0aed1452084f5c89793cad91b17aea11","tid":651481,"uid":148028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:36:59.000Z","msg":"我自己set目標多數都係set距離而唔係時間<br />\n<br />\n啱啱開始跑可以set 2-3km, 之後再慢慢加<br />\n<br />\n速度方面就要你自己去感受, 用一個唔會扯曬蝦但又唔會太hea嘅速度跑（記住均速！唔好時快時慢）<br />\n<br />\n建議dl番個跑步app (例如Runkeeper), 開著gps佢就會幫你計到個速度"},{"pid":"a07926109ef0db4922007d5167e5c1775e189b95","tid":651481,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:41:46.000Z","msg":"一開頭跑下，跑到無氣，停下行下再跑，每次四十分鍾<br />\n咁樣隔日跑<br />\n<br />\n之後慢慢推一次過跑既時間推長<br />\n<br />\n到一次過跑到三十分鐵就轉做一星期2～3次就得<br />\n<br />\n最好每次跑到四十分鍾"},{"pid":"5580b2f160dbeb97efbeb10ba0130e30e7c40532","tid":651481,"uid":180348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T08:44:40.000Z","msg":"老實講，如果想減肥或者純粹剩係想強身健體，跑步已經過時，effective差好多<br />\n建議你去健身，你唔想做resistant training既，可以做HIIT"},{"pid":"9bcb34dc05c162f3ca560e451e50ef24464233d8","tid":651481,"uid":24982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,